     The Outpost is a hybrid RTS, successfully combining elements of
     Real Time Strategy, Random Roguelike events and Chaos Management,
     where players never play through the game quite the same way twice.

     You and your crew are stranded on a frozen Mining Outpost, you must
     fight, build and explore to survive. Earthquakes, freezing storms
     and the local wildlife are bad enough, but something killed the
     last occupants of this base, and it'll be back..

     Will you save the day? Or save yourself?
